OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FOften
OL,6,Fcloudy on Saturday with sunny
OL,7,Fintervals and perhaps the odd shower.
OL,8,FBecoming increasingly settled and dry
OL,9,Fthereafter with lengthy periods of
OL,10,Fsunshine on Sunday and Monday. Turning
OL,11,Fwarmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
